high_descs: Head rotate and turn left to the fridge.
Turn right to the mug.
Pick the mug from the microwave.
Place the mug in the microwave.
Turn left and turn right to the sidetable.
Pick the mug from the table.
Turn left to the microwave rack.
Turn right and place the mug in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To place the mug in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around to the middle of the room and turn right to the end of the passage and head to the fridge on the right.
Pick up the mug from the fridge.
Turn around to reach the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave.
Turn right to reach the passage and walk to the bedroom on the right of the passage to reach the sidetable.
Pick up the mug from the dresser.
Turn right to exit the room and turn left to walk down the passage and turn right to head to the microwave.
Put the mug in the microwave with the other mug.
anns.task_desc: Put two Mug in the Microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk through the hall way to your right head towards the steel rack, then turn right and go to the fridge to your left.
Get the mug out of the fridge.
Turn around to the countertop to your back side and to the microwave.
Put the mug into the microwave.
Turn around and enter into the hallway to your left, then hang a right walk into the bedroom, and go to the sidetable to your right.
Pick up the mug from the side table.
Turn around and go to the hallway to your left, then hang a right and head towards the microwave on the countertop to your right.
Put the mug into the microwave besides the other mug.
anns.task_desc: Put two mugs into the microwave
